      • getRawData

        public java.util.Vector<SensorData> getRawData(java.util.Date time,
                                               boolean plusMinusOneSecond)
        Get raw data fro the given time stamp. If data one second before and after the given time shall be included as well the plusMinusOneSecond flag shall be set. Note to easily convert between a unix time stamp and the Date object one can use the provided Utils.unixToDate(int) function.
        Parameters:
        time - the time to search raw data for
        plusMinusOneSecond - in case this flag is set the data recorded one second earlier and later will be included as well
        Returns:
        a vector containing the data sets that meet the requirements
